subject: Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
Automobile Racing
lead_paragraph: Trevor Bayne did not earn Sprint Cup series points for his Daytona 500 victory because he isn’t racing at the top level full-time. But the Wood Brothers, hope to change that.
